{"tid":446920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《文匯》跟蹤學生動源召集人鍾翰林　學生動源發聲明譴責","createTime":"2017-10-24T18:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T06:20:04.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a7586cce96fec880f62649b7fc863fb257ef33","tid":446920,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"獨派學生團體「學生動源」發表聲明，譴責《文匯報》跟蹤召集人鍾翰林，侵犯其個人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》今早以〈神秘交收「獨」品 「學動」再禍校園〉為題，以狗仔隊式跟蹤獨派學生團體「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林；並報道鍾翰林與疑似「本土工作室」負責人見面，交收有關香港獨立的宣傳品。<br />\n<br />\n報道顯示，該報記者於本月20日跟蹤鍾翰林放學後一舉一動，由下午4時放學，至5時許到天水圍交收，再跟蹤鍾翰林至元朗住所。報道甚至提及鐘翰林與友人通電內容，並刊出「本土工作室」相關人士及鍾翰林住所的大門。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」發聲明譴責《文匯報》嚴重侵犯組織召集人鍾翰林個人私隱，並指「等絕不畏懼任何騷擾」，會繼續將港獨聲音帶入校園。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E8%B7%9F%E8%B9%A4%E9%8D%BE%E7%BF%B0%E6%9E%97-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%BA%90%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E8%25B7%259F%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E9%258D%25BE%25E7%25BF%25B0%25E6%259E%2597-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25BA%2590%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%2F&d=Q8pdFaTDdXkZv1Z8oTHUCW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=58b78ad7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E8%25B7%259F%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E9%258D%25BE%25E7%25BF%25B0%25E6%259E%2597-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25BA%2590%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%2F&h=5f2c2f29\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E8%B7%9F%E8%B9%A4%E9%8D%BE%E7%BF%B0%E6%9E%97-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%BA%90%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC/</a>"},{"pid":"f5fa81b247bcbf6309a5b78364b0f1ed4896936d","tid":446920,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":